виней</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>herd of pigs</q></tr></example><example xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg><lang/></usg><quote>xutæ ærdongtæj cæwuncæ</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>свиньи ходят стадами</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>pigs walk in herds</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Сл."/></bibl></example><example><quote>ǧæwama “Svinovodʼ' xuti ærdongtæ sxæccæ kæna 1.9 mil. wængæ</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>«Свиновод» должен довести стада свиней до 1.9 милл.</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>(the programme) “Svinovod” is expected to increase the number of pig herds up to 1.9 mil.</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_FS"/><biblScope>V 24</biblScope></bibl></example><example><quote>ūdonmæ dærdʒæf xyztīs x˳yty styr ærdong</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>вдали же от них паслось большое стадо свиней</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>there was a good way off from them an herd of many swine feeding</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Матфей"/><biblScope>%i8%i 30</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ce"><lang/> <w>ardanga</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/> <w>ording</w> <gloss><q>стая</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘шайка’. Дальнейшее не ясно. <bibl><author>Benveniste (</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_BSL"/><biblScope>LII 33)</biblScope></bibl> связывает с <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/> <w>drang-</w> <gloss><q>крепко держать</q></gloss></mentioned>; фонетически это очень неплохо, но развитие значения не совсем ясно. Ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ræǧaw"/> | ærǧaw, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_bal"/>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Compare <mentioned xml:lang="ce"><lang/> <w>ardanga</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/> <w>ording</w> <gloss><q>pack</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘gang’. Дальнейшее не ясно. <bibl><author>Benveniste (</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_BSL"/><biblScope>LII 33)</biblScope></bibl> connects the word with <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/> <w>drang-</w> <gloss><q>to hold tight</q></gloss></mentioned>; it is quite good on the phonetics part, but the development of the meaning is not quite clear. See <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ræǧaw"/> | ærǧaw, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_bal"/>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>